<subSubSection id="C350B2B199378545E887FD6ED7D8F3A5" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99378545E887FD6ED76DF2C5" blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" box="[151,572,656,683]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899378545E887FD6ED743F2C5" bold="true" box="[151,530,656,683]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Number of specimens recorded.</emphasis>
21.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99378545E8D7FD4BD7D0F29A" blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899378545E8D7FD4BD430F2A1" bold="true" box="[199,353,692,719]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Distribution.</emphasis>
Thus far only recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="F35DA1AA99378545EAA1FD4AD7A0F2A1" box="[689,753,693,719]" name="Spain" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Spain</collectingCountry>
and North Africa. 
<collectingCountry id="F35DA1AA99378545EBD7FD4AD17BF2A1" box="[967,1066,693,719]" name="Portugal" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: one province (Douro Litoral) in this study, and Algarve (Dyte unpubl. data).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99378545E8D7FD02D4C8F3ED" blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899378545E8D7FD02D47DF379" bold="true" box="[199,300,765,791]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Ecology.</emphasis>
In 
<collectingCountry id="F35DA1AA99378545E940FD02D4E3F379" box="[336,434,765,791]" name="Portugal" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Portugal</collectingCountry>
, this species has been collected in fair numbers in agricultural land (with greenhouses) on sandy soil, and in an area with a mosaic of habitats from dunes to forest, riparian corridors and agricultural fields; one specimen was retrieved from a sandy spit at the mouth of the river Douro. Its ecology in the rest of its distribution range is unknown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99378545E8D7FC73D499F3C9" blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" box="[199,456,908,935]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899378545E8D7FC73D400F3C9" bold="true" box="[199,337,908,935]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
3.4 (rare).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF5E13A99378545E8D7FC4FD7D8F3A5" blockId="49.[151,1436,656,972]" box="[199,649,944,972]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis id="B93E3D2899378545E8D7FC4FD4D3F3A5" bold="true" box="[199,386,944,971]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Activity period.</emphasis>
June, (mainly) August.
</paragraph>
